snippet: A Maine supreme court justice says a cellphone company turned over more than 50,000 text messages in a divorce case in which a protection order was in place....

headline.print_headline: 50,000 Texts Handed Over in Maine Divorce Case
headline.main: 50,000 Texts Handed Over in Maine Divorce Case

lead_paragraph: A Maine supreme court justice says a cellphone company turned over more than 50,000 text messages in a divorce case in which a protection order was in place.
